Create a 30-second real-estate Reel script with exactly 5 scenes for: {{$json.topic}}.

Return this exact JSON structure:
{
  "title": "<catchy reel title>",
  "hook": "<opening hook text overlay, max 8 words>",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "scene_number": 1,
      "image_prompt": "<detailed photorealistic image description, 9:16 vertical, ultra-realistic architectural photography>",
      "voice_line": "<voiceover text, max 15 words>"
    }
  ],
  "cta": "<call-to-action text overlay, max 8 words>"
}
